{"tid":1284800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣戰】政府扮慘，我地要比佢更慘 - 一齊整合慘情文宣","createTime":"2019-07-04T10:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T10:22:01.000Z","uid":9448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0a3842013d3634bfde1abca01af511f11ed5d26d","tid":1284800,"uid":9448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:21:11.000Z","msg":"借人account。其實呢位巴打講得幾啱，係中立派同某啲外國人眼中，而家有少少輿論係真係去咗以武制暴係唔係<span style=\"color: red;\">morally right</span>呢個問題上面。<br />\n<br />\n[重要］依家真係民意戰劣勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1284191\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1284191</a><br />\n<br />\n尤其睇開紅底媒體嗰啲（<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">外國有好多媒體其實已經被染紅左</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）親耳聽到有外國人話I think their requests are reasonable and I support them. But I think there must be a better way than violence to do things. 講真其實<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好多外媒既用詞都對我地好不利</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n【唔好咁快開心住】外媒報緊香港既野大部分都醜化緊我地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276520</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大部分人都係鍾意鋤強扶弱。我地爭取支持嘅時候要扮吓慘（其實講個真相出嚟已經夠慘，都唔使扮）。對<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鍾意站喺道德高地指責暴力嘅人，令佢哋可以扶持弱小係最容易得到返佢哋嘅支持</span></span>。唔使同佢地講咁多理性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n之前好成功嘅一次文宣係毛EE同義士嘅呢段對話。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t4L3Q2z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft4L3Q2z.png&h=f3405837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有巴打將個晚救死士既片cut左出黎加中英文字幕。呢段片睇一次喊一次，我覺得我地可以集中宣傳一下。<br />\n見到個view而家都係得38K，唔係太多人睇過。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KVIP8ohKvDI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKVIP8ohKvDI&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI2rU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=56b25c6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KVIP8ohKvDI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲有冇睇過一啲會牽起人同情心嘅片段或者相？ 大家一齊整合一下做文宣。"},{"pid":"d14131ca533597953739c11da2cc420242602868","tid":1284800,"uid":54228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OE22naf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOE22naf.png&h=850a8f27&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}